Interface SpecificStatusViewer

All Known Implementing Classes:
CLIGameOverViewer, CLIGamePreparationViewer, CLILoginViewer, CLINumberPlayerViewer, CLIPlayingViewer, CLIReadyViewer, CLIResumeGameViewer, CLIStatusViewer, CLIWaitingViewer, GUIGameOverStatus, GUIGamePreparation, GUILoginStatus, GUINewGame, GUINumberPlayerStatus, GUIPlaying, GUIReadyStatus, GUIResumeRequest, GUIResumingGame, GUIStatusViewer, GUIWaitingtatus, TerminalLoginStatus, TerminalNumberPlayerViewer, TerminalReadyStatus, TerminalStatusViewer, TerminalWaitingStatus, WTerminalGamePreparationViewer, WTerminalLoginViewer, WTerminalNumberPlayerViewer, WTerminalPlayingViewer, WTerminalReadyViewer, WTerminalResumeGameViewer, WTerminalStatusViewer, WTerminalWaitingViewer
public interface SpecificStatusViewer
Interface implemented by all the Classes implementing any specific StatusViewer. It'll be useful either to set common methods and to have all those similar Classes implementing a same interface.
